## FEATURES

• **LIVE STAT SYNC** – Auto-updates after each match
• **HISTORICAL DATA** – Track progress across seasons
• **WEAPON ANALYSIS** – See which guns you're best with
• **LANDING SPOT STATS** – Best drop locations for you
• **SESSION TRACKING** – Performance by play session
• **PEAK HOURS** – When you play your best
• **FRIEND COMPARE** – Leaderboards with friends
• **PDF EXPORT** – Share reports with coaches
• **GOAL SETTING** – Track toward milestones
• **ALERTS** – Notify when you beat records
• **NO EPIC LOGIN NEEDED** – Works with any username

